      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n  - Individuals/ societies/ self-help groups/ associations/ reservoir monopolies/ private units etc. involved in inland fisheries activities can avail the benefits of inland schemes.\n  - The applicant should be a Fisherman.\n  - The applicant should belong to the Schedule Tribe(ST) category.\n  - Applicant should be above 18 years of age.\n  - The beneficiary fisherman must have his own bank account.\n\n",
